quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  3,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  3,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  3,2,khuda ( jo mabood brhq hai ) is ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi hamesha zindah rehne wala
  3,3,is ne ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum par sachhi kitaab nazil ki jo pehli ( aasmani ) kitabon ki tasdeeq karti hai aur isi ne torat aur injeel nazil ki
  3,4,( yani ) logon ki hadaayat ke liye pehlay ( torat aur injeel utari ) aur ( phir quran jo haq aur baatil ko ) allag allag kar dainay wala ( hai ) nazilkiya jo log khuda ki aayton ka inkaar karte hain un ko sakht azaab hoga aur khuda zabardast ( aur ) badla lainay wala hai
  3,5,khuda ( aisa khaibar o baseer hai ke ) koi cheez is se posheeda nahi nah zameen mein aur nah aasman mein
  3,6,wohi to hai jo ( maa ke pait mein ) jaisi chahta hai tumhari soorten banata hai is ghalib hikmat walay ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi
  3,7,wohi to hai jis ne tum par kitaab nazil ki jis ki baaz ayatain mohakam hain ( aur ) wohi asal kitaab hain aur baaz mutshabeh hain to jin logon ke dilon mein kajji hai woh mutashbihaat ka itebaa karte hain taakay fitnah barpaa karen aur morad asli ka pata lagayen halaank morad asli khuda ke siwa koi nahi jaanta aur jo log ilm mein dast gaah kaamil rakhtay hain woh yeh kehte hain ke hum un par imaan laaye yeh sab hamaray perwar-digaar ki taraf se hain aur nasiyaat to aqal mand hi qubool karte hain
  3,8,ae perwar-digaar jab to ne hamein hadaayat bakhsh hai to is ke baad hamaray dilon mein kajji nah peda kar dejyu aur hamein apne haan se Nemat ataa farma to to bara ataa frmane wala hai
  3,9,ae perwar-digaar! to is roz jis ( ke anay ) mein kuch bhi shak nahi sab logon ko ( apne huzoor mein ) jama karle ga be shak khuda khilaaf wada nahi karta
  3,10,jo log kafir hue ( is din ) nah to un ka maal hi khuda ( ke azaab ) se un ko bacha sakay ga aur nah un ki aulaad hi ( kuch kaam aeye gi ) aur yeh log aatish ( jahannum ) ka eendhan hon ge
  3,11,un ka haal bhi firounion aur un se pehlay logon ka sa hoga jinhon ne hamari aayton ki takzieeb ki thi to khuda ne un ko un ke gunaaho ke sabab ( azaab mein ) pakar liya tha aur khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
  3,12,( ae paighambar ) kafiroon se kehdo ke tum ( duniya mein bhi ) anqareeb maghloob ho jao ge aur ( akhirat mein ) jahannum ki taraf hankay jao ge aur woh buri jagah hai
  3,13,tumahray liye do garohoon mein jo ( jung badar ke din ) aapas mein bhir gay ( qudrat khuda ki azeem al shan ) nishani thi aik giroh ( musalmanoon ka tha woh ) khuda ki raah mein lar raha tha aur dosra giroh ( kafiroon ka tha woh ) un ko apni aankhon se apne se dugna mushahida kar raha tha aur khuda apni nusrat se jis ko chahta hai madad deta hai jo ahal Basarat hain un ke liye is ( waqeye ) mein barri Ibrat hai
  3,14,logon ko un ki khawahishon ki cheeze yani aurtain aur betay aur sonay aur chandi ke barray barray dhair aur nishaan lagey hue ghoray aur maweshi aur khaiti barri zeenat daar maloom hoti hain ( magar ) yeh sab duniya hi ki zindagi ke samaan hain aur khuda ke paas bohat acha thikana hai
  3,15,( ae paighambar un se ) kaho ke bhala mein tum ko aisi cheez batau jo un cheezon se kahin achi ho ( suno ) jo log parhaizgaar hain un ke liye khuda ke haan baagaat ( bahisht ) hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain un mein woh hamesha rahen ge aur pakeeza aurtain hain aur ( sab se barh kar ) khuda ki khushnodi aur khuda ( apne naik ) bundon ko dekh raha hai
  3,16,jo khuda se iltija karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum imaan le aeye so hum ko hamaray gunah maaf farma aur dozakh ke azaab se mehfooz rakh
  3,17,yeh woh log hain jo ( mushkilaat mein ) sabr karte aur sach boltay aur ibadat mein lagey rehtay aur ( raah khuda mein ) kharch karte aur auqaat sehar mein gunaaho ki maffi manga karte hain
  3,18,khuda to is baat ki gawahi deta hai ke is ke siwa koi mabood nahi aur farishtay aur ilm walay log jo insaaf par qaim hain woh bhi ( gawahi dete hain ke ) is ghalib hikmat walay ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi
  3,19,deen to khuda ke nazdeek islam hai aur ahal kitaab ne jo ( is deen se ) ikhtilaafkiya to ilm honay ke baad aapas ki zid sekiya aur jo shakhs khuda ki aayton ko nah manay to khuda jald hisaab lainay wala ( aur saza dainay wala ) hai
  3,20,ae paighambar agar yeh log tum se jhagrnay lagen to kehna ke mein aur mere pairo to khuda ke farmanbardar ho chuke aur ahal kitaab aur un parh logon se kaho kekiya tum bhi ( khuda ke farmanbardar bantay ho ) aur islam laatay ho? agar yeh log islam le ayen to be shak hadaayat paleen aur agar ( tumhara kaha ) nah manen to tumhara kaam sirf khuda ka pegham pouncha dena hai aur khuda ( apne ) bundon ko dekh raha hai
  3,21,jo log khuda ki aayton ko nahi mantay aur anbia ko na-haq qatal karte rahay hain aur jo insaaf ( karne ) ka hukum dete hain inhen bhi maar daaltay hain un ko dukh dainay walay azaab ki khushkhabri suna do
  3,22,yeh aisay log hain jin ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein barbaad hain aur un ka koi madadgaar nahi ( hoga )
  3,23,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jin ko kitaab ( khuda yani torat se ) behra diya gaya aur woh ( is ) kitaab allah ki taraf bulaye jatay hain taakay woh ( un ke tanazuath ka ) un mein faisla kar day to aik fareeq un mein se kaj adai ke sath munh phair laita hai
  3,24,yeh is liye ke yeh is baat ke qaail hain ke ( dozakh ki ) aag hamein chand roz ke siwa chhoo hi nahi sakay gi aur jo kuch yeh deen ke baray mein bohtan bandhte rahay hain is ne un ko dhokay mein daal rakha hai
  3,25,to is waqtkiya haal hoga jab hum un ko jama karen ge ( yani ) is roz jis ( ke anay ) mein kuch bhi shak nahi aur har nafs apne aamaal ka poora poora badla paye ga aur un par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
  3,26,kaho ke ae khuda ( ae ) badshahi ke maalik to jis ko chahay badshahi bakhshay aur jis se chahay badshahi chean le aur jis ko chahay izzat day aur jisay chahay zaleel kere har terhan ki bhalai tairay hi haath hai aur be shak to har cheez par Qadir hai
  3,27,to hi raat ko din mein daakhil karta aur to hi din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai to hi be jaan se jandaar peda karta hai aur to hi jandaar se be jaan peda karta hai aur tuhi jis ko chahta hai be shumaar rizaq bkhshta hai
  3,28,mominon ko chahiye ke mominon ke siwa kafiroon ko dost nah banayen aur jo aisa kere ga is se khuda ka kuch ( ehad ) nahi haan agar is tareeq se tum un ( ke shar ) se bachao ki soorat peda karo ( to muzaiqa nahi ) aur khuda tum ko apne ( ghazab ) se darata hai aur khuda hi ki taraf ( tum ko ) lout kar jana hai
  3,29,( ae paighambar logon se ) keh do ke koi baat tum apne dilon mein makhfi rakho ya usay zahir karo khuda is ko jaanta hai aur jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai is ko sab ki khabar hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  3,30,jis din har shakhs apne aamaal ki neki ko mojood paley ga aur un ki buraiee ko bhi ( dekh le ga ) to arzoo kere ga ke ae kash is mein aur is buraiee mein daur ki masafat ho jati aur khuda tum ko apne ( ghazab ) se darata hai aur khuda apne bundon par nihayat meharban hai
  3,31,( ae paighambar logon se ) keh do ke agar tum khuda ko dost rakhtay ho to meri pairwi karo khuda bhi tumhe dost rakhay ga aur tumahray gunah maaf kar day ga aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  3,32,keh do ke khuda aur is ke rasool ka hukum manu agar nah manen to khuda bhi kafiroon ko dost nahi rakhta
  3,33,khuda ne aadam aur Nooh aur khandan ibrahim aur khandan Imran ko tamam Jahan ke logon mein munhtakhib farmaya tha
  3,34,un mein se baaz baaz ki aulaad they aur khuda suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  3,35,( woh waqt yaad karne ke Laiq hai ) jab Imran ki biwi ne kaha ke ae perwar-digaar jo ( bacha ) mere pait mein hai mein is ko teri Nazar karti hon usay duniya ke kamon se azad rakhon gi to ( usay ) meri taraf se qubool farma toto suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  3,36,jab un ke haan bacha peda howa aur jo kuch un ke haan peda howa tha khuda ko khoob maloom tha to kehnay lagen ke perwar-digaar! mere to larki hui hai aur ( Nazar ke liye ) larka ( mozoon tha ke woh ) larki ki terhan ( naatvaan ) nahi hota aur mein ne is ka naam maryam rakha hai aur mein is ko aur is ki aulaad ko shetan mardood se teri panah mein deti hon
  3,37,to perwar-digaar ne is ko pasandeedgi ke sath qubool farmaya aur usay achi terhan parwarishkiya aur zikria ko is ka mutakaffil banaya zikria jab kabhi ibadat gaah mein is ke paas jatay to is ke paas khana paate ( yeh kefiyat dekh kar aik din maryam se ) poochnay lagey ke maryam yeh khana tumahray paas kahan se aata hai woh bolein khuda ke haan se ( aata hai ) bay shak khuda jisay chahta hai be shumaar rizaq deta hai
  3,38,is waqt zikria ne apne perwar-digaar se dua ki ( aur ) kaha ke perwar-digaar mujhe apni janab se aulaad Saleh ataa farma to be shak dua suneney ( aur qubool karne ) wala hai
  3,39,woh abhi ibadat gaah mein kharray namaz hi parh rahay they ke firshton ne aawaz di ke ( zikria ) khuda tumhe yahya ki basharat deta hai jo khuda ke Faiz yani ( eesa ) ki tasdeeq karen ge aur sardar hon ge aur aurton se raghbat nah rakhnay walay aur ( khuda ke ) paighambar ( yani ) naiko karon mein hon ge
  3,40,zikria ne kaha ae perwar-digaar mere haan larka kyonkr peda hoga ke mein to budha hogaya hon aur meri biwi banjh hai khuda ne farmaya isi terhan khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  3,41,zikria ne kaha ke perwar-digaar ( mere liye ) koi nishani muqarrar farma khuda ne farmaya nishani yeh hai ke tum logon se teen din isharay ke siwa baat nah kar sakuu ge to ( un dinon mein ) apne perwar-digaar ki kasrat se yaad aur subah o shaam is ki tasbeeh karna
  3,42,aur jab firshton ne ( maryam se ) kaha ke maryam! khuda ne tum ko bargzidakiya hai aur pak banaya hai aur Jahan ki aurton mein munhtakhibkiya hai
  3,43,maryam apne perwar-digaar ki farmabardari karna aur sajda karna aur ruku karne walon ke sath ruku karna
  3,44,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) yeh baatein akhbar ghaib mein se hain jo hum tumahray paas bhaijtay hain aur jab woh log apne qalam ( bator quraa ) daal rahay they ke maryam ka متکفل kon banay to tum un ke paas nahi they aur nah is waqt hi un ke paas they jab woh aapas mein jhagar rahay they
  3,45,( woh waqt bhi yaad karne ke Laiq hai ) jab firshton ne ( maryam se kaha ) ke maryam khuda tum ko apni taraf se aik Faiz ki basharat deta hai jis ka naam maseeh ( aur mashhoor ) eesa Ibn maryam hoga ( aur ) jo duniya aur akhirat mein ba aabro aur ( khuda ke ) khason mein se hoga
  3,46,aur maa ki goad mein aur barri Umar ka ho kar ( dono halaton mein ) logon se ( yaksaa ) guftagu kere ga aur naiko karon mein hoga
  3,47,maryam ne kaha perwar-digaar mere haan bacha kyonkr hoga ke kisi ensaan ne mujhe haath taq to lagaya nahi farmaya ke khuda isi terhan jo chahta hai peda karta hai jab woh koi kaam karna chahta hai to irshad farma deta hai ke hoja to woh ho jata hai
  3,48,aur woh inhen likhna ( parhna ) aur danai aur torat aur injeel sikhayiye ga
  3,49,aur ( eesa ) bani Israel ki taraf paighambar ( ho kar jayen ge aur kahin ge ) ke mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aaya hon woh yeh ke tumahray samnay matti ki mourat bashakal parind banata hon phir is mein phoonk maarta hon to woh khuda ke hukum se ( sach mach ) janwar ho jata hai aur andhay aur abras ko tandrost kar deta hon aur khuda ke hukum se murdy mein jaan daal deta hon aur jo kuch tum kha kar atay ho aur jo apne gharon mein jama kar rakhtay ho sab tum ko bta deta hon agar tum sahib imaan ho to un baton mein tumahray liye ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishani hai
  3,50,aur mujh se pehlay jo torat ( nazil hui ) thi is ki tasdeeq bhi karta hon aur ( mein ) is liye bhi ( aaya hon ) ke baaz cheeze jo tum par haraam theen un ko tumahray liye halal kar dun aur mein to tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aaya hon to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  3,51,kuch shak nahi ke khuda hi mera aur tumhara perwar-digaar hai to isi ki ibadat karo yahi seedha rasta hai
  3,52,jab eesa ne un ki taraf se nafarmani aur ( niyat qatal ) dekhi to kehnay lagey ke koi hai jo khuda ka taraf daar aur mera madadgaar ho hawari bolay ke hum khuda ke ( tarafdar aur aap ke ) madadgaar hain hum khuda par imaan laaye aur aap gawah rahen ke hum farmanbardar hain
  3,53,ae perwar-digaar jo ( kitaab ) to ne nazil farmai hai hum is par imaan le aeye aur ( tairay ) paighambar ke muttabe ho chuke to hum ko maan-ne walon mein likh rakh
  3,54,aur woh ( yani yahood qatal eesa ke baray mein aik ) chaal chalay aur khuda bhi ( eesa ko bachanay ke liye ) chaal chala aur khuda khoob chaal chalne wala hai
  3,55,is waqt khuda ne farmaya ke eesa! mein tumhari duniya mein rehne ki muddat poori karkay tum ko apni taraf utha lon ga aur tumhe kafiroon ( ki sohbat ) se pak kar dun ga aur jo log tumhari pairwi karen ge un ko kafiroon par qayamat taq Faiq ( o Ghalib rakhon ga phir tum sab mere paas lout kar aao ge to jin baton mein tum ikhtilaaf karte they is din tum mein un ka faisla kardoon ga
  3,56,yani jo kafir hue un ko duniya aur akhirat ( dono ) mein sakht azaab dun ga aur un ka koi madadgaar nah hoga
  3,57,aur jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ko khuda poora poora sila day ga aur khuda zaalmon ko dost nahi rakhta
  3,58,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) yeh hum tum ko ( khuda ki ) ayatain aur hikmat bhari nsihtin parh parh kar sunaate hain
  3,59,eesa ka haal khuda ke nazdeek aadam ka sa hai ke is ne ( pehlay ) matti se un ka Qalib banaya phir farmaya ke ( ensaan ) ho ja to woh ( ensaan ) ho gay
  3,60,( yeh baat ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona
  3,61,phir agar yeh log eesa ke baray mein tum se jhagra karen aur tum ko haqeeqat al haal to maloom ho hi chali hai to un se kehna ke aao hum apne biton aur aurton ko bulayen tum apne biton aur aurton ko bulaao aur hum khud bhi ayen aur tum khud bhi aao phir dono fareeq ( khuda se ) duao iltaja ا karen aur jhuton par khuda ki laanat bhejen
  3,62,yeh tamam bayanaat sahih hain aur khuda ke siwa koi mabood nahi aur bay shak khuda ghalib aur sahib hikmat hai
  3,63,to agar yeh log phir jayen to khuda mfsdon ko khoob jaanta hai
  3,64,keh do ke ae ahal kitaab jo baat hamaray aur tumahray dono ke darmain yaksaa ( tasleem ki gayi ) hai is ki taraf aao woh yeh ke khuda ke siwa hum kisi ki ibadat nah karen aur is ke sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah banayen aur hum mein se koi kisi ko khuda ke siwa apna car saaz nah samjhay agar yeh log ( is baat ko ) nah manen to ( un se ) keh do ke tum gawah raho ke hum ( khuda ke ) farmaa bardaar hain
  3,65,ae ehley kitaab tum ibrahim ke baray mein kyun jhagarte ho halaank torat aur injeel un ke baad utri hain ( aur woh pehlay ho chuke hain ) tokiya tum aqal nahi rakhtay
  3,66,dekho aisi baat mein to tum ne jhagrakiya hi tha jis ka tumhe kuch ilm tha bhi magar aisi baat mein kyun jhagarte ho jis ka tumhe kuch bhi ilm nahi aur khuda jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  3,67,ibrahim nah to yahodi they aur nah isaai balkay sab se be talluq ho kar aik ( khuda ) ke ho rahay they aur isi ke farmaa bardaar they aur mushrikon mein nah they
  3,68,ibrahim se qurb rakhnay walay to woh log hain jo un ki pairwi karte hain aur paighambar ( Akhir uz zaman ) aur woh log jo imaan laaye hain aur khuda mominoun ka karsaaz hai
  3,69,( ae ahal islam ) baze ehley kitaab is baat ki khwahish rakhtay hain ke tum ko gumraah kar den magar yeh ( tum kokiya gumraah karen ge ) apne aap ko hi gumraah kar rahay hain aur nahi jantay
  3,70,ae ehley kitaab tum khuda ki aayton se kyun inkaar karte ho aur tum ( torat ko ) mantay to ho
  3,71,ae ehley kitaab tum sach ko jhoot ke sath khalt malt kyun karte ho aur haq ko kyun chupatay ho aur tum jantay bhi ho
  3,72,aur ehley kitaab aik dosray se kehte hain ke jo ( kitaab ) mominoun par nazil hui hai is par din ke shuru mein to imaan le aaya karo aur is ke aakhir mein inkaar kar diya karo taakay woh ( islam se ) bur-ghashta ho jayen
  3,73,aur apne deen ke pairo ke siwa kisi aur ke qaail nah hona ( ae paighambar ) keh do ke hadaayat to khuda hi ki hadaayat hai ( woh yeh bhi kehte hain ) yeh bhi ( nah maanna ) ke jo cheez tum ko mili hai waisi kisi aur ko miley gi ya woh tumhe khuda ke rubaroo qaail maqool kar saken ge yeh bhi keh do ke buzurgi khuda hi ke haath mein hai woh jisay chahta hai deta hai aur khuda kashaish wala ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  3,74,woh apni rehmat se jis ko chahta hai khaas kar laita hai aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  3,75,aur ehley kitaab mein se koi to aisa hai ke agar tum is ke paas ( rupoo ka ) dhair amanat rakh do to tum ko ( foran ) wapas day day aur koi is terhan ka hai ke agar is ke paas aik dinar bhi amanat rakho to jab taq is ke sir par har waqt kharray nah raho tumhe day hi nahi yeh is liye ke woh kehte hain ke ummiyon ke baray mein hum se muwakhza nahi hoga yeh khuda par mehez jhoot boltay hain aur ( is baat ko ) jantay bhi hain
  3,76,haan jo shakhs apne iqraar ko poora kere aur ( khuda se ) daray to khuda darny walon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,77,jo log khuda ke iqraron aur apni qasmon ( ko beech daaltay hain aur un ) ke aiwz thori si qeemat haasil karte hain un ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi un se khuda nah to kalaam kere ga aur nah qayamat ke roz un ki taraf dekhe ga aur nah un ko pak kere ga aur un ko dukh dainay wala azaab hoga
  3,78,aur un ( ehley kitaab ) mein baze aisay hain ke kitaab ( torat ) ko zabaan maror maror kar parhte hain taakay tum samjhoo ke jo kuch woh parhte hain kitaab mein se hai halaank woh kitaab mein se nahi hai aur kehte hain ke woh khuda ki taraf se ( nazil howa ) hai halaank woh khuda ki taraf se nahi hota aur khuda par jhoot boltay hain aur ( yeh baat ) jantay bhi hain
  3,79,kisi aadmi ko Shayaan nahi ke khuda to usay kitaab aur hukoomat aur nabuwat ataa farmaiye aur woh logon se kahe ke khuda ko chore kar mere bande ho jao balkay ( is ko yeh kehna sazawar hai ke ae ehley kitaab ) tum ( ulmaye ) Rabbani ho jao kyunkay tum ktabِ ( khuda ) parhte parhatay rehtay ho
  3,80,aur is ko yeh bhi nahi kehna chahiye ke tum firshton aur payghambaroon ko khuda banalo bhala jab tum musalman ho chuke tokiya usay zaiba hai ke tumhe kafir honay ko kahe
  3,81,aur jab khuda ne payghambaroon se ehad liya ke jab mein tum ko kitaab aur danai ataa karoon phir tumahray paas koi paighambar aeye jo tumhari kitaab ki tasdeeq kere to tumhen zaroor is par imaan lana hoga aur zaroor is ki madad karni hogi aur ( ehad lainay ke baad ) poocha ke bhala tum ne iqraarkiya aur is iqraar par mera zimma liya ( yani mujhe zamin t_hraya ) unhon ne kaha ( haan ) hum ne iqraarkiya ( khuda ne ) farmaya ke tum ( is ehad o paymaan ke ) gawah raho aur mein bhi tumahray sath gawah hon
  3,82,to jo is ke baad phir jayen woh bad kirdaar hain
  3,83,kiya yeh ( kafir ) khuda ke deen ke siwa kisi aur deen ke taalib hain halaank sab ehley aasman o zameen khusi ya zabardasti se khuda ke farmaa bardaar hain aur isi ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  3,84,kaho ke hum khuda par imaan laaye aur jo kitaab hum par nazil hui aur jo saheefay ibrahim aur ismael aur ashq aur Yaqoob aur un ki aulaad par utre aur jo kitaaben moose aur eesa aur dosray anbia ko perwar-digaar ki taraf se milein sab par imaan laaye hum un payghambaroon mein se kisi mein kuch farq nahi karte aur hum isi ( khuday-e wahid ) ke farmaa bardaar hain
  3,85,aur jo shakhs islam ke siwa kisi aur deen ka taalib hoga woh is se hargiz qubool nahikiya jaye ga aur aisa shakhs akhirat mein nuqsaan uthany walon mein hoga
  3,86,khuda aisay logon ko kyonkr hadaayat day jo imaan laane ke baad kafir hogaye aur ( pehlay ) is baat ki gawahi day chuke ke yeh paighambar brhq hai aur un ke paas dalail bhi aagaye aur khuda be insafon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  3,87,un logon ki saza yeh hai ke un par khuda ki aur firshton ki aur insanon ki sab ki laanat ho
  3,88,hamesha is laanat mein ( girftar ) rahen ge un se nah to azaab halkakiya jaye ga aur nah inhen mohlat day jaye gi
  3,89,haan jinhon ne is ke baad tauba ki aur apni haalat durust kar li to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  3,90,jo log imaan laane ke baad kafir ho gay phir kufar mein barhatay gay aison ki tauba hargiz qubool nah hogi aur yeh log gumraah hain
  3,91,jo log kafir hue aur kufar hi ki haalat mein mar gay woh agar ( nijaat haasil karni chahain aur ) badlay mein zameen bhar kar sona den to hargiz qubool nahkiya jaye ga un logon ko dukh dainay wala azaab ho ga aur un ki koi madad nahi kere ga
  3,92,( momino! ) jab taq tum un cheezon mein se jo tumhen Aziz hain ( raah e khuda mein ) sirf nah karo ge kabhi neki haasil nah kar sakuu ge aur jo cheez tum sirf karo ge khuda is ko jaanta hai
  3,93,bani Israel ke liye ( torat ke nazil honay se ) pehlay khanay ki tamam cheeze halal theen bajuz un ke jo Yaqoob ne khud apne oopar haraam kar li theen keh do ke agar sachey ho to torat lao aur usay padho ( yani Daleel paish karo )
  3,94,jo is ke baad bhi khuda par jhutay aftara karen to aisay log hi be insaaf hain
  3,95,keh do ke khuda ne sach farmaya diya pas deen ibrahim ki pairwi karo jo sab se be talluq ho kar aik ( khuda ) ke ho rahay they aur mushrikon se nah they
  3,96,pehla ghar jo logon ( ke ibadat karne ) ke liye muqarrarkiya gaya tha wohi hai jo mukkay mein hai babarkat aur jahan ke liye mojab hadaayat
  3,97,is mein khuli hui nishanain hain jin mein se aik ibrahim ke kharray honay ki jagah hai jo shakhs is ( mubarak ) ghar mein daakhil howa is ne aman pa liya aur logon par khuda ka haq ( yani farz ) hai ke jo is ghar taq jaane ka Maqdoor rakhay woh is ka hajj kere aur jo is hukum ki tameel nah kere ga to khuda bhi ehley aalam se be niaz hai
  3,98,kaho ke ehley kitaab! tum khuda ki aayton se kyun kufar karte ho aur khuda tumahray sab aamaal se bakhabar hai
  3,99,kaho ke ehley kitaab tum mominoun ko khuda ke raste se kyun roktay ho aur bawajood yeh ke tum is se waaqif ho is mein kajji nikaltay ho aur khuda tumhare kamon se be khabar nahi
  3,100,momino! agar tum ehley kitaab ke kisi fareeq ka kaha maan lau ge to woh tumhen imaan laane ke baad kafir bana den ge
  3,101,aur tum kyonkr kufar karo ge jabkay tum ko khuda ki ayatain parh parh kar sunai jati hain aur tum mein is ke paighambar mojood hain aur jis ne khuda ( ki hadaayat ki rassi ) ko mazboot pakar liya woh seedhay raste lag gaya
  3,102,momino! khuda se daro jaissa ke is se darny ka haq hai aur marna to musalman hi marna
  3,103,aur sab mil kar khuda ki ( hadaayat ki rassi ) ko mazboot pakdae rehna aur mutafarraq nah hona aur khuda ki is meharbani ko yaad karo jab tum aik dosray ke dushman they to is ne tumahray dilon mein ulfat daal di aur tum is ki meharbani se bhai bhai hogaye aur tum aag ke garhay ke kinare taq poanch chuke they to khuda ne tum ko is se bacha liya is terhan khuda tum ko apni ayatain khol khol kar sunataa hai taakay tum hadaayat pao
  3,104,aur tum mein aik jamaat aisi honi chahiye jo logon ko neki ki taraf bulaye aur achay kaam karne ka hukum day aur buray kamon se mana kere yahi log hain jo nijaat panay walay hain
  3,105,aur un logon ki terhan nah hona jo mutafarraq ho gay aur ehkaam bain anay ke baad aik dosray se ( khilaaf o ) ikhtilaaf karne lagey yeh woh log hain jin ko qayamat ke din bara azaab hoga
  3,106,jis din bohat se munh safaid hon ge aur bohat se munh siyah to jin logon ke munh siyah hon ge ( un se khuda farmaiye ga )kiya tum imaan laa kar kafir hogaye they? so ( ab ) is kufar ke badlay azaab ( ke mazay ) chako
  3,107,aur jin logon ke munh safaid hon ge woh khuda ki rehmat ( ke baghoon ) mein hon ge aur un mein hamesha rahen ge
  3,108,yeh khuda ki ayatain hain jo hum tum ko sahet ke sath parh kar sunaate hain aur khuda ehley aalam par zulm nahi karna chahta
  3,109,aur jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai aur sab kamon ka rujoo ( aur injaam ) khuda hi ki taraf hai
  3,110,( momino ) jitni ummatain ( yani qoumain ) logon mein peda huien tum un sab se behtar ho ke naik kaam karne ko kehte ho aur buray kamon se mana karte ho aur khuda par imaan rakhtay ho aur agar ehley kitaab bhi imaan le atay to un ke liye bohat acha hota un mein imaan laane walay bhi hain ( lekin thoray ) aur aksar nafarman hain
  3,111,aur yeh tumhe khafee FC takleef ke siwa kuch nuqsaan nahi pouncha saken ge aur agar tum se lrhin ge to peeth phair kar bhaag jayen ge phir un ko madad bhi ( kahin se ) nahi miley gi
  3,112,yeh jahan nazar ayen ge zillat ( ko dekho ge ke ) un se chimat rahi hai bajuz is ke ke yeh khuda aur ( musalman ) logon ki panah mein aa jayen aur yeh log khuda ke ghazab mein girftar hain aur nadari un se lapat rahi hai yeh is liye ke khuda ki aayton se inkaar karte they aur ( is ke ) payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal kar dete they yeh is liye ke yeh nafarmani kiye jatay aur hadd se barhay jatay they
  3,113,yeh bhi sab aik jaisay nahi hain un ehley kitaab mein kuch log ( hukm-e khuda par ) qaim bhi hain jo raat ke waqt khuda ki ayatain parhte aur ( is ke agay ) sajda karte hain
  3,114,( aur ) khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay aur achay kaam karne ko kehte aur buri baton se mana karte aur nakiyon par lapaktay hain aur yahi log nekokaar hain
  3,115,aur yeh jis terhan ki neki karen ge is ki naqadri nahi ki jaye gi aur khuda parhaiz garon ko khoob jaanta hai
  3,116,jo log kafir hain un ke maal aur aulaad khuda ke ghazab ko hargiz nahi taall saken ge aur yeh log ehley dozakh hain ke hamesha isi mein rahen ge
  3,117,yeh jo maal duniya ki zindagi mein kharch karte hain is ki misaal howa ki si hai jis mein sakht sardi ho aur woh aisay logon ki khaiti par jo apne aap par zulm karte they chalay aur usay tabah kar day aur khuda ne un par kuch zulm nahikiya balkay yeh khud apne oopar zulm kar rahay hain
  3,118,momino! kisi ghair ( mazhab ke aadmi ) ko apna raazadan nah banana yeh log tumhari kharabi aur ( fitnah angazi karne ) mein kisi terhan ki kotahi nahi karte aur chahtay hain ke ( jis terhan ho ) tumhe takleef puhanche un ki zabanon se to dushmani zahir hohi chuki hai aur jo ( kinay ) un ke seenon mein makhfi hain woh kahin ziyada hain agar tum aqal rakhtay ho to hum ne tum ko apni ayatain khol khol kar suna di hain
  3,119,dekho tum aisay ( saaf dil ) log ho ke un logon se dosti rakhtay ho halaank woh tum se dosti nahi rakhtay aur tum sab kitabon par imaan rakhtay ho ( aur woh tumhari kitaab ko nahi mantay ) aur jab tum se mlitay hain to kehte hain hum imaan le aeye aur jab allag hotay hain to tum par ghusse ke sabab ungelian kaat kaat khatay hain ( un se ) keh do ke ( badbakhto ) ghusse mein mar jao khuda tumahray dilon ki baton se khoob waaqif hai
  3,120,agar tumhe aasoudgi haasil ho to un ko buri lagti hai aur agar ranj puhanche to khush hotay hain aur agar tum tklifon ki bardasht aur ( un se ) kinara kashi karte raho ge to un ka fraib tumhen kuch bhi nuqsaan nah pouncha sakay ga yeh jo kuch karte hain khuda is par ihata kiye hue hai
  3,121,aur ( is waqt ko yaad karo ) jab tum subah ko apne ghar rawana ho kar imaan walon ko larai ke liye morchon par ( mauqa bah mauqa ) mutayyan karne lagey aur khuda sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai
  3,122,is waqt tum mein se do jamaaton ne jee chore dena chaha magar khuda un ka madadgaar tha aur mominoun ko khuda hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye
  3,123,aur khuda ne jang-e badar mein bhi tumhari madad ki thi aur is waqt bhi tum be saro vsaman they pas khuda se daro ( aur un ehsaanon ko yaad karo ) taakay shukar karo
  3,124,jab tum mominoun se yeh keh ( kar un ke dil barha ) rahay they kekiya yeh kaafi nahi ke perwar-digaar teen hazaar farishtay nazil kar ke tumhe madad day
  3,125,haan agar tum dil ko mazboot rakho aur ( khuda se ) drtay raho aur kafir tum par josh ke sath دفعتہ hamla kar dein to perwar-digaar paanch hazaar farishtay jin par nishaan hon ge tumhari madad ko beje ga
  3,126,aur is madad ko khuda ne tumhare liyezarya basharat banaya yani is liye ke tumahray dilon ko is se tasalii haasil ho warna madad to khuda hi ki hai jo ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  3,127,( yeh khuda ne ) is liye (kiya ) ke kafiroon ki aik jamaat ko halaak ya inhen zaleel o maghloob kar day ke ( jaisay aeye they waisay hi ) nakaam wapas jayen
  3,128,( ae paighambar ) is kaam mein tumhara kuch ikhtiyar nahi ( ab do soorten hain ) ya khuda unkay haal par meharbani kere ya inhen azaab day ke yeh zalim log hain
  3,129,aur jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai woh jisay chahay bakhash day aur jisay chahay azaab kere aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  3,130,ae imaan walo! dugna chuguna sood nah khao aur khuda se daro taakay nijaat haasil karo
  3,131,aur ( dozakh ki ) aag se bachcho jo kafiroon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai
  3,132,aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki itaat karo taakay tum par rehmat ki jaye
  3,133,apne perwar-digaar ki bakhshish aur bahisht ki taraf lapko jis ka arz aasman aur zameen ke barabar hai aur jo ( khuda se ) darny walon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai
  3,134,jo aasoudgi aur tangi mein ( apna maal khuda ki raah mein ) kharch karte hain aur ghusse ko roktay aur logon ke qasoor maaf karte hain aur khuda naiko karon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,135,aur woh ke jab koi khula gunah ya apne haq mein koi aur buraiee kar baithtay hain to khuda ko yaad karte aur apne gunaaho ki bakhshish mangte hain aur khuda ke siwa gunah bakhash bhi kon sakta hai? aur jaan boojh kar apne af-aal par uray nahi rehtay
  3,136,aisay hi logon ka sila perwar-digaar ki taraf se bakhshish aur baagh hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain ( aur ) woh un mein hamesha baste rahen ge aur ( achay ) kaam karne walon ka badla bohat acha hai
  3,137,tum logon se pehlay bhi bohat se waqeat guzar chuke hain to tum zameen ki sair karkay dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka kaisa injaam howa
  3,138,yeh ( quran ) logon ke liye bayan Sarih aur ehley taqwa ke liye hadaayat aur nasiyaat hai
  3,139,aur ( dekho ) be dil nah hona aur nah kisi terhan ka gham karna agar tum momin ( Sadiq ) ho to tum hi ghalib raho ge
  3,140,agar tumhe zakham ( shikast ) laga hai to un logon ko bhi aisa zakham lag chuka hai aur yeh din hain ke hum un ko logon mein bdalty rehtay hain aur is se yeh bhi maqsood tha ke khuda imaan walon ko mutamayyaz kar de aur tum mein se gawah banaye aur khuda be insafon ko pasand nahi karta
  3,141,aur yeh bhi maqsood tha ke khuda imaan walon ko khalis ( momin ) bana day aur kafiroon ko nabood kar day
  3,142,kiya tum yeh samajte ho ke ( be azmaish ) bahisht mein ja daakhil ho ge halaank abhi khuda ne tum mein se jehaad karne walon ko to achi terhan maloomkiya hi nahi aur ( yeh bhi maqsood hai ) ke woh saabit qadam rehne walon ko maloom kere
  3,143,aur tum mout ( shahadat ) ke anay se pehlay is ki tamannakiya karte they so tum ne is ko aankhon se dekh liya
  3,144,aur Mohammad ( sale allah aleh wasallam ) to sirf ( khuda ke ) paighambar hain un se pehlay bhi bohat se paighambar ho guzray hain bhala agar yeh mar jayen ya maaray jayen to tum ultay paon phir jao? ( yani murtid ho jao? ) aur jo ultay paon phir jaye ga to khuda ka kuch nuqsaan nah kar sakay ga aur khuda shukar guzaron ko ( bara ) sawab day ga
  3,145,aur kisi shakhs mein taaqat nahi ke khuda ke hukum ke baghair mar jaye ( is ne mout ka ) waqt muqarrar kar ke likh rakha hai aur jo shakhs duniya mein ( apne aamaal ka ) badla chahay is ko hum yahin badla day den ge aur jo akhirat mein talbِ sawab ho is ko wahan ajar ataa karen ge aur hum shukar guzaron ko anqareeb ( bohat acha ) sila den ge
  3,146,aur bohat se nabi hue hain jin ke sath ho kar aksar ahal allah ( khuda ke dushmanon se ) larray hain to jo musibtain un par raah e khuda mein waqay huien un ke sabab unhon ne nah to himmat haari aur nah buzdali ki nah ( kafiroon se ) dabey aur khuda istiqlal rakhnay walon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,147,aur ( is haalat mein ) un ke munh se koi baat nikalti hai to yahi ke ae perwar-digaar hamaray gunah aur zyadtyan jo hum apne kamon mein karte rahay hain maaf farma aur hum ko saabit qadam rakh aur kafiroon par fatah inayat farma
  3,148,to khuda ne un ko duniya mein bhi badla diya aur akhirat mein bhi bohat acha badla ( day ga ) aur khuda naiko karon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,149,momino! agar tum kafiroon ka kaha maan lau ge to woh tum ko ultay paon phair kar ( murtid kar ) den ge phir tum barray khasaray mein par jao ge
  3,150,( yeh tumahray madadgaar nahi hain ) balkay khuda tumhara madadgaar hai aur woh sab se behtar madadgaar hai
  3,151,hum anqareeb kafiroon ke dilon mein tumhara roab bitha den ge kyunkay yeh khuda ke sath shirk karte hain jis ki is ne koi bhi Daleel nazil nahi ki aur un ka thikana dozakh hai woh zaalmon ka bohat bُra thikana hai
  3,152,aur khuda ne apna wada sacha kar diya ( yani ) is waqt jabkay tum kafiroon ko is ke hukum se qatal kar rahay they yahan taq ke jo tum chahtay they khuda ne tum ko dikha diya is ke baad tum ne himmat haar di aur hukum ( paighambar ) mein jhagra karne lagey aur is ki nafarmani ki baaz to tum mein se duniya ke khawastgah they aur baaz akhirat ke taalib is waqt khuda ne tum ko un ( ke muqablay ) se phair ( kar bhaga ) diya taakay tumhari azmaish kere aur is ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya aur khuda momino par bara fazl karne wala hai
  3,153,( woh waqt bhi yaad karne ke Laiq hai ) jab tum log daur bhage jatay they aur kisi ko peechay phir kar nahi dekhte they aur rasool allah tum ko tumahray peechay kharray bulaa rahay they to khuda ne tum ko gham par gham pohanchaya taakay jo cheez tumahray haath se jati rahi ya jo museebat tum par waqay hui hai is se tum andoh naak nah ho aur khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  3,154,phir khuda ne gham o ranj ke baad tum par tasalii nazil farmai ( yani ) neend ke tum mein se aik jamaat par taari ho gayi aur kuch log jin ko jaan ke lale par rahay they khuda ke baray mein na-haq ( ayyaam ) kufar ke se gumaan karte they aur kehte they bhala hamaray ikhtiyar ki kuch baat hai? tum keh do ke be shak sab baatein khuda hi ke ikhtiyar mein hain yeh log ( bohat si baatein ) dilon mein makhfi rakhtay hain jo tum par zahir nahi karte they kehte they ke hamaray bas ki baat hoti to hum yahan qatal hi nah kiye jatay keh do ke agar tum apne gharon mein bhi hotay to jin ki taqdeer mein mara jana likha tha woh apni apni qatal gaahon ki taraf zaroor nikal atay is se gharz yeh thi ke khuda tumahray seenon ki baton ko aazamaa_e aur jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai is ko khalis aur saaf kar day aur khuda dilon ki baton se khoob waaqif hai
  3,155,jo log tum mein se ( Ahad ke din ) jabkay ( mominoun aur kafiroon ki ) do jamaten aik dosray se guth gayeen ( jung se ) bhaag gaye to un ke baaz af-aal ke sabab shetan ne un ko phsla diya magar khuda ne un ka qasoor maaf kar diya be shak khuda bakhsnay wala aur Burdbar hai
  3,156,momino! un logon jaisay nah hona jo kufar karte hain aur un ke ( musalman ) bhai jab ( khuda ki raah mein ) safar karen ( aur mar jayen ) ya jehaad ko nikleen ( aur maaray jayen ) to un ki nisbat kehte hain ke agar woh hamaray paas rehtay to nah martay aur nah maaray jatay. un baton se maqsood yeh hai ke khuda un logon ke dilon mein afsos peda kar day aur zindagi aur mout to khuda hi deta hai aur khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
  3,157,aur agar tum khuda ke raste mein maaray jao ya marjao to jo ( maal o mata ) log jama karte hain is se khuda ki bakhshish aur rehmat kahin behtar hai
  3,158,aur agar tum marjao ya maaray jao khuda ke huzoor mein zaroor ikhatay kiye jao ge
  3,159,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) khuda ki meharbani se tumhari aftad mizaaj un logon ke liye naram waqay hui hai. aur agar tum badkhu aur sakht dil hotay to yeh tumahray paas se bhaag kharray hotay. to un ko maaf kardo aur un ke liye ( khuda se ) mughfirat mango. aur apne kamon mein un se mashwarat liya karo. aur jab ( kisi kaam ka ) azm musammam karlo to khuda par bhrosa rakho. be shak khuda bhrosa rakhnay walon ko dost rakhta hai
  3,160,aur khuda tumhara madadgaar hai to tum par koi ghalib nahi aasakta. aur agar woh tumhe chore day to phir kon hai ke tumhari madad kere aur mominoun ko chahiye ke khuda hi par bhrosa rakhen
  3,161,aur kabhi nahi ho sakta ke paighambar ( khuda ) khayanat karen. aur khayanat karne walon ko qayamat ke din khayanat ki hui cheez ( khuda ke rubaroo ) la hazir karni hogi. phir har shakhs ko is ke aamaal ka poora poora badla diya jaye ga aur be insafi nahi ki jaye gi
  3,162,"bhala jo shakhs khuda ki khushnodi ka tabay ho woh is shakhs ki terhan ( murtakib khayanat ) ho sakta hai jo khuda ki na khushi mein girftar ho aur jis ka thikana dozakh hai, aur woh bura thikana hai"
  3,163,un logon ke khuda ke haan ( mukhtalif aur mutafawat ) darjay hain aur khuda un ke sab aamaal ko dekh raha hai
  3,164,khuda ne mominoun par bara ahsaankiya hai ke un mein inhen mein se aik paighambar beje. jo un ko khuda ki ayatain parh parh kar sunaate aur un ko pak karte aur ( khuda ki ) kitaab aur danai sikhate hain aur pehlay to yeh log Sarih gumraahi mein they
  3,165,( bhala yeh )kiya ( baat hai ke ) jab ( Ahad ke din kafir ke haath se ) tum par museebat waqay hui halaank ( jung badar mein ) is se dochnd museebat tumahray haath se un par prhchki hai توتم chala utthay ke ( haae ) aafat ( hum par ) kahan se aa parri keh do ke yeh tumhari hi shamat aamaal hai ( ke tum ne paighambar ke hukum ke khilaafkiya ) be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  3,166,aur jo museebat tum par dono jamaaton ke muqablay ke din waqay hui so khuda ke hukum se ( waqay hui ) aur ( is se ) yeh maqsood tha ke khuda mominoun ko achi terhan maloom
  3,167,aur mnafqon ko bhi maloom karle aur ( jab ) un se kaha gaya ke aao khuda ke raste mein jung karo ya ( kafiroon ke ) hamlon ko roko. to kehnay lagey ke agar hum ko larai ki khabar hoti to hum zaroor tumahray sath rehtay yeh is din imaan ki nisbat kufar se ziyada qareeb they munh se woh baatein kehte hain jo un ke dil mein nahi hain. aur jo kuch yeh chupatay hain khuda un se khoob waaqif hai
  3,168,yeh khud to ( jung se bach kar ) baith hi rahay they magar ( jinhon ne raah khuda mein jaanen qurbaan kar dein ) apne ( un ) bhaiyon ke baray mein bhi kehte hain ke agar hamara kaha mantay to qatal nah hotay. keh do ke agar sachey ho to apne oopar se mout ko taall dena
  3,169,jo log khuda ki raah mein maaray gay un ko marey hue nah samjhna ( woh marey hue nahi hain ) balkay khuda ke nazdeek zindah hain aur un ko rizaq mil raha hai
  3,170,jo kuch khuda ne un ko apne fazl se bakhash rakha hai is mein khush hain. aur jo log un ke peechay reh gay aur ( shaheed hokar ) un mein shaamil nahi hosakay un ki nisbat khusihyan mana rahay hain ke ( qayamat ke din ) un ko bhi nah kuch khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge
  3,171,aur khuda ke inamaat aur fazl se khush ho rahay hain. aur is se ke khuda mominoun ka ajar zaya nahi karta
  3,172,jinhon ne bawajood zakham khanay ke khuda aur rasool ( ke hukum ) ko quboolkiya jo log un mein nekokaar aur parhaizgaar hain un ke liye bara sawab hai
  3,173,( jab ) un se logon ne aakar bayankiya ke kufar ne tumahray ( muqablay ke ) liye lashkar kaseer ) jamakiya hai to un se daro. to un ka imaan aur ziyada hogaya. aur kehnay lagey hum ko khuda kaafi hai aur woh bohat acha karsaaz hai
  3,174,phir woh khuda ki nematon aur is ke fazl ke sath ( khush vkhrm ) wapas aeye un ko kisi terhan ka zarrar nah pouncha. aur woh khuda ki khushnodi ke tabay rahay. aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  3,175,yeh ( khauf dilanay wala ) to shetan hai jo apne doston se darata hai to agar tum momin ho to un se mat darna aur mujh hi se drtay rehna
  3,176,aur jo log kufar mein jaldi karte hain un ( ki wajah ) se ghamgeen nah hona. yeh khuda ka kuch nuqsaan nahi kar saktay khuda chahta hai ke akhirat mein un ko kuch hissa nah day aur un ke liye bara azaab tayyar hai
  3,177,jin logon ne imaan ke badlay kufar khareeda woh khuda ka kuch nahi bigaar satke aur un ko dukh dainay wala azaab hoga
  3,178,aur kafir log yeh nah khayaal karen ke hum jo un ko mohlat diye jatay hain to yeh un ke haq mein acha hai. ( nahi balkay ) hum un ko is liye mohlat dete hain ke aur gunah karlen. aakhir kaar un ko zaleel karne wala azaab hoga
  3,179,( logo ) jab taq khuda napak ko pak se allag nah kardey ga mominoun ko is haal mein jis mein tum ho hargiz nahi rehne day ga. aur allah tum ko gaib ki baton se bhi mutala nahi kere gaalbt_h khuda apne payghambaroon mein se jisay chahta hai intikhab karleta hai. to tum khuda par aur is ke rasoloo par imaan lao aur agar imaan lao ge aur parhaiz gari karo ge to tum ko ajar azeem miley ga
  3,180,jo log maal mein jo khuda ne apne fazl se un ko ataa farmaya hai bukhal karte hain woh is bukhal ko apne haq mein acha nah samjhain. ( woh acha nahi ) balkay un ke liye bura hai woh jis maal mein bukhal karte hain qayamat ke din is ka taoq bana kar un ki gardnon mein dala jaye ga. aur asmano aur zameen ka waris khuda hi hai. aur jo amal tum karte ho Khuda ko maloom hai
  3,181,khuda ne un logon ka qoul sun liya hai jo kehte hain ke khuda faqeer hai. aur hum Ameer hain. yeh jo kehte hain hum is ko likh len ge. aur payghambaroon ko jo yeh na-haq qatal karte rahay hain is ko bhi ( qalamband kar rakhen ge ) aur ( qayamat ke roz ) kahin ge ke azaab ( aatish ) sozaa ke mazay chahkte raho
  3,182,yeh un kamon ki saza hai jo tumahray haath agay bhaijtay rahay hain aur khuda to bundon par mutlaq zulm nahi karta
  3,183,jo log kehte hi ke khuda ne hamein hukum bheja hai ke jab taq koi paighambar hamaray paas aisi niaz le kar nah aeye jis ko aag aakar kha jaye tab taq hum is par imaan nah layein ge ( ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke mujh se pehlay kayi paighambar tumahray paas khuli hui nishanain le kar aeye aur woh ( moujza ) bhi laaye jo tum kehte ho to agar sachey ho to tum ne un ko qatal kyunkiya ?
  3,184,phir agar yeh log tum ko sacha nah samjhain to tum se pehlay bohat se paighambar khuli hui nishanain aur saheefay aur roshan kitaaben le kar aachukay hain aur logon ne un ko bhi sacha nahi samgha
  3,185,har mutnaqas ko mout ka maza chakhna hai aur tum ko qayamat ke din tumahray aamaal ka poora poora badla diya jaye ga. to jo shakhs aatish jahannum se daur rakha gaya aur bahisht mein daakhilkiya gaya woh morad ko poanch gaya aur duniya ki zindagi to dhokay ka samaan hai
  3,186,( ae ahal imaan ) tumahray maal o jaan mein tumhari azmaish ki jaye gi. aur tum ahal kitaab se aur un logon se jo mushriq hain bohat si aeza ki baatein suno ge. aur to agar sabr aur parhaiz gari karte raho ge to yeh barri himmat ke kaam hain
  3,187,aur jab khuda ne un logon se jin ko kitaab inayat ki gayi thi iqraar karliya ke ( jo kuch is mein likha hai ) usay saaf saaf bayan karte rehna. aur is ( ki kisi baat ) ko nah chhupana to anhn ne is ko pas pusht pheink diya aur is ke badlay thori si qeemat haasil ki. yeh jo kuch haasil karte hain bura hai
  3,188,jo log apne ( napasand ) kamon se khush hotay hain aur pasandeeda kaam ) jo karte nahi un ke liye chahtay hain ke un kaaf tareef ki jaye un ki nisbat khayaal nah karna ke woh azaab se rastgaar ho jaien ge. aur inhen dard dainay wala azaab hoga
  3,189,aur asmano aur zameen ki badshahi khuda hi ko hai aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  3,190,be shak asmano aur zameen ki paidaiesh aur raat aur din ke badal badal ke anay jaane mein aqal walon ke liye nishanain hain
  3,191,jo kharray aur baithy aur letey ( har haal mein ) khuda ko yaad karte aur aasman aur zameen ki paidaiesh mein ghhor karte ( aur kehte hain ) ke ae perwar-digaar! to ne is ( makhlooq ) ko be faida nahi pedakiya to pak hai to ( qayamat ke din ) hamein dozakh ke azaab se bchayyo
  3,192,ae perwar-digaar jis ko to ne dozakh mein dala usay ruswakiya aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
  3,193,ae پروردگارہم ne aik nida karne walay ko suna ke imaan ke liye pukaar raha tha ( yani ) apne perwar-digaar par imaan lao to hum imaan le aeye ae perwar-digaar hamaray gunah maaf farma aur hamari buraiyon ko hum se mehv kar aur hum ko duniya se naik bundon ke sath utha
  3,194,ae perwar-digaar to ne jin jin cheezon ke hum se apne payghambaroon ke zariye se waday kiye hain woh hamein ataa farma aur qayamat ke din hamein ruswa nah کیجو kuch shak nahi ke to khilaaf wada nahi karta
  3,195,to un ke perwar-digaar ne un ki dua qubool kar li ( aur farmaya ) ke mein kisi amal karne walay ke amal ko mard ho ya aurat zaya nahi karta tum aik dosray ki jins ho to jo log mere liye watan chore gay aur apne gharon se nikalay gay aur sataye gay aur larray aur qatal kiye gay mein un ke gunah daur kardoon ga aur un ko bahishtoon mein daakhil karoon ga jin ke neechay nehrain bah rahi hain ( yeh ) khuda ke haan se badla hai aur khuda ke haan acha badla hai
  3,196,( ae paighambar ) kafiroon ka shehron mein chalna phirna tumhe dhoka nah day
  3,197,( yeh duniya ka ) thora sa faida hai phir ( akhirat mein ) to un ka thikana dozakh hai aur woh buri jagah hai
  3,198,lekin jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay rahay un ke liye baagh hai jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain ( aur ) un mein hamesha rahen ge ( yeh ) khuda ke haan se ( un ki ) mehmani hai aur jo kuch khuda ke haan hai woh naiko karon ke liye bohat acha hai
  3,199,aur baaz ehley kitaab aisay bhi hain jo khuda par aur is ( kitaab ) par jo tum par nazil hui aur is par jo un par nazil hui imaan rakhtay hain aur khuda ke agay aajzi karte hain aur khuda ki aayton ke badlay thori si qeemat nahi letay yahi log hain jin ka sila un ke perwar-digaar ke haan tayyar hai aur khuda jald hisaab lainay wala hai
  3,200,ae ahal imaan ( kufar ke muqablay mein ) saabit qadam raho aur istiqamat rakho aur
